.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-REMOTE-HTLC-TOTAL-MSAT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-remote-htlc-total-msat \- FEAT-2045 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-remote-htlc-total-msat
.SH DESCRIPTION
channel-remote-htlc-total-msat for lightning CLI (FEAT-2045).
.PP
Sums the total amount in millisatoshis of all incoming (remote) HTLCs
across all peer channels by querying listpeerchannels.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
